## Content Strategy Summary

**Post Categories:**
- **Educational:** Scientific research, proven methods (Monday-1, Tuesday-1, Thursday-1, Sunday-2)
- **Practical:** Tips, strategies, tactics (Monday-2, Tuesday-3, Wednesday-2, Thursday-2)
- **Awareness:** Statistics, facts, myths debunked (Monday-3, Wednesday-1, Thursday-1, Friday-2)
- **Engaging:** Gamification, interactive content, motivation (Wednesday-3, Thursday-3, Friday-3, Saturday-3)

**HabitForm Features Highlighted:**
- Probabilistic Habit Formation algorithm (Monday-1, Thursday-1, Sunday-2)
- Habit Heatmap (Monday-3, Tuesday-2)
- Streaks (Current/Longest) (Tuesday-1, Wednesday-2, Friday-1, Sunday-1)
- Share feature (Friday-2)
- Flexible Reminders (Monday-2, Tuesday-3, Wednesday-1, Saturday-1)
- Customization (Wednesday-3, Saturday-3, Sunday-3)
- Detailed Statistics (Tuesday-1, Friday-1, Sunday-1)

**CTA Strategy:**
Each CTA includes these elements:
1. Feature emphasis (what it does)
2. Benefit (what you gain)
3. Call to action (download, use, start)
4. Urgency/speed factor (now, instantly, in 1 minute)

